room_title: Escape room "Defenders of the Galaxy" by Xscape Pods in Los Angeles
room_address: 4200 Chino Hills Pkwy #825 Chino Hills, CA 91709
room_description: You and your crew were transporting a Power stone needed to Defend the Galaxy, when you were attacked. You managed to destroy the alien ships, but your ship lost its engines during the battle. Does your crew have what it takes to fix the ship and escape from the gravity of the star? You have one hour to find out where your zany crew hid the backup batteries needed to restart the engine and use the Power Stone to active your new warp core.
